; Regression test for issue #636: Budget report query doesn't generate correct report (BZ#636)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/636
; When using a query (account name filter) with the budget command,
; only accounts matching the query should appear in the report.

~ Monthly
    Expenses:Food    $500.00
    Expenses:Books   $100.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/10 Store
    Expenses:Food    $300.00
    Expenses:Books    $80.00
    Assets:Cash

test budget -p "2024/01"
    $-380.00     $-600.00      $220.00   63%  Assets:Cash
     $380.00      $600.00     $-220.00   63%  Expenses
      $80.00      $100.00      $-20.00   80%    Books
     $300.00      $500.00     $-200.00   60%    Food
------------ ------------ ------------ -----
           0            0            0     0
end test

test budget -p "2024/01" Food
     $300.00      $500.00     $-200.00   60%  Expenses:Food
end test
